8 Support Polls That Show That Donald Trump Is Serious
Some have tried to brand him as a wind breeze.
Others think he's just a joke.
Some are waiting for collapse.
While some Republicans have tried to squeeze Donald Trump off the top of the support polls, it hasn’t (yet) succeeded.
Of the last 11 national surveys, 10 have been led by Donald Trump in the two-digit number, and some have begun to seriously consider what this means for the real estate king’s nomination opportunities.
Of course, the election is only in the early stages.
These results do not mean that Trump is likely to become a Republican candidate.
